                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9802" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1478</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">745 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">运输企业如何借数字化管理解决增值税抵扣“痛点”？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Breaking Through Difficulties and Seeking Paths: Value-added Tax Planning for &quot;Company + Farmer&quot; Type Transportation Enterprises in the Context of Digitalization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨霞，段文轩，续彬，钟捷麒，马成慧，赵茂，杨晓涓，康萍</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南寻甸龙华实业有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">运输企业；数字化管理；增值税筹划</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Transportation enterprise;Digital management;Value-added tax planning</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例讲述了“公司+农户”型国有运输公司——H公司如何通过对现有的管理体系进行数字化改革来解决在增值税抵扣上的“痛点”。作为轻资产运营企业，H公司与拥有运输车辆的农户合作完成日常运输工作，但在成本占比较大的通行费问题上一度面临通行费票据难以收集且难证明其发生的真实合规性的困难。这一问题直接造成H公司无法正常进行进项税额抵扣，进而需要将这一部分税务负担通过涨价转移到客商身上，从而导致公司在市场竞争中处于劣势的局面。痛定思痛，公司高管提出了两种数字化管理方案来解决增值税筹划问题，通过对比分析方案各自的特点和意义，从而选定最好的解决之法。本案例旨在引导学生学习税收筹划的原理和方法，学会正确解读税收政策，并结合企业自身的特点和需求，思考如何合法合规地为企业降低税务负担和涉税风险？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">TThis case study tells the story of H Company, a state-owned transportation company operating under the &quot;company + farmer&quot; model, and how it addressed the &quot;pain point&quot; of VAT deduction by digitalizing its existing management system. As a light-asset operation enterprise, H Company collaborates with farmers who own transport vehicles to handle daily transportation tasks. However, it once faced difficulties in collecting toll receipts and proving their authenticity and compliance, which directly led to the company&#39;s inability to normally deduct input VAT. As a result, H Company had to pass on this tax burden to customers through price hikes, putting it at a disadvantage in market competition. After a thorough reflection, the company&#39;s senior management proposed two digital management solutions to solve the VAT planning problem. By comparing and analyzing the characteristics and significance of each solution, the best approach was selected. This case aims to guide students in learning the principles and methods of tax planning, correctly interpreting tax policies, and considering how to legally and compliantly reduce the tax burden and tax-related risks for enterprises based on their own characteristics and needs.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《税收筹划》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">税务筹划；增值税原理；主营业务利润</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
